name: Quetzalcoatl’s_Temple_2D[05][Prototype_02]
description:
Prototype[02]
Some dreams hold deeper meaning, an understanding of things we cannot comprehend whit our “wake” minds, this story started as such… a dream? Quetzalcoatl, the flying feathered God serpent in Mexican mythology, the creator of mankind, keeper of boundaries between earth and heaven. 
As the vision goes, I was invited into a ceremony at his temple, hidden in space and time at his birthplace. This structure resembles the morphologic configuration of such temple, as I have seen it, where time, space and dimensions are linked between the curling of his flying paths. 

Jpg 1080x1080 mp4 @arquiaz
